The point of comparison here is that the Word will show us what needs to be cleansed and amended in our lives, as the iniri-or in regard to our bodies. It shows us what we actually are in conti-ast with what our deceitful heart paints us (ver. 26) ; it shows us also what is the true ideal of humanity which we are called upon to realize in our lives.
